{
  "stem": "24171.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So one was for the women fixed and the other one was for the men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They closed up-- I mean, opened the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they made the small, little window kind of just the women should know where the davening is-- what would you call it?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't know how to say it in English-- you know, the [INAUDIBLE], the [INAUDIBLE] the minyan, the davening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was just two of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was my girlfriend's father and [INAUDIBLE] and my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Them two just could read the Torah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was an Orthodox home?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, real Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [INAUDIBLE] was [INAUDIBLE] where we went to-- to buy the other necessary things for the house, and like your clothing could be too, and the smaller thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for the real one is [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mukacheve. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately, I-- I forgot about how much the kilometers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go to the train like an hour and a half and then to [INAUDIBLE], and that just by walking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from [INAUDIBLE] took an hour for the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In between was little villages just kind of thing, though.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it took an hour.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I had girlfriends, a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I said, they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I specially when was kind of with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not just me, there were-- a lot of the youngsters were kind of-- they-- we were like-- but there was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like for instance, when the children were small.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When they were bigger, that's OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you know when children are small, I don't know, in Yiddish, we have a-- a have a saying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know if I should say it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are saying, [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what it mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
